com.interpss.core.aclf.adj

Interface SwitchedShunt

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfControlBus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PVBusLimit, RemoteQBus
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StaticVarCompensator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StaticVarCompensatorImpl, SwitchedShuntImpl

    public interface SwitchedShunt
extends RemoteQBus
    A representation of the model object 'Switched Shunt'. for representing switched shunt devices

    The following features are supported:

    • Control Mode
    • BInit
    • Desired Voltage Range
    • Var Bank Array
    See Also:
    AclfAdjustPackage.getSwitchedShunt()
